u00f3ng VTV3|publisher=vtv.vn|accessdate=March 23, 2020}}</ref></small>\n| ''[[:vi:T\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng|T\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng]]'' <br/><small>(Love and Ambition)</small>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 56\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | VFC\n| B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn Huy (director); \u0110an Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, C\u1ea5m H\u1eb1ng, Mai Di\u1ec7p (writers); Nhan Ph\u00fac Vinh, Di\u1ec5m My, M\u1ea1nh Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, L\u00e3 Thanh Huy\u1ec1n, Thanh S\u01a1n, Minh Huy\u1ec1n, Tr\u1ecdng Trinh, Minh H\u00f2a, Di\u1ec5m H\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n B\u00edch, Thanh T\u00fa, Th\u00f9y Anh, Phan Th\u1eafng...\n| ''N\u1eafm'' <br><small>(Hold)</small><br><small>by H\u01b0\u01a1ng Ly & Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng M4U</small><br/>\n| Drama, Romance\n| <small>Based on Chinese drama 'Fighting Time'</small>\n|}\n\n====Wednesday-Friday dramas====\nStarting on 7 Feb 2020, VTV adds Friday prime-time to this time slot.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://baomoi.com/tang-lich-phat-song-phim-tren-khung-gio-vang-cua-vtv3/c/33895126.epi|title=T\u0103ng l\u1ecbch ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng phim tr\u00ean khung gi\u1edd v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a VTV3|publisher=baomoi|accessdate=February 7, 2020}}</ref>\n\nThese dramas air from 21h30 to 22h20, Wednesday to Friday on [[VTV3]] instead of only Wednesday and Thursday as before.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! style=\"width:10%;\"| Broadcast\n! style=\"width:24%;\"| Title\n! style=\"width:6%;\"| Eps.\n! style=\"width:5%;\"| Prod.\n! style=\"width:25%;\"| Cast and crew\n! style=\"width:20%;\"| Theme song(s)\n! style=\"width:5%;\"| Genre\n! style=\"width:5%;\"| Notes\n|----- bgcolor=\"#ebf5ff\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |15 Jan-18 Mar <br><small><ref>{{cite web|url=https://vtv.vn/truyen-hinh/co-gai-nha-nguoi-ta-bo-phim-tuoi-tre-goi-nhieu-cam-xuc-va-mang-huong-vi-dac-biet-20191230183340531.htm|title=C\u00f4 g\u00e1i nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta: B\u1ed9 phim tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb g\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 mang h\