iet-20191230183340531.htm|title=C\u00f4 g\u00e1i nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta: B\u1ed9 phim tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb g\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 mang h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t|publisher=vtv.vn|accessdate=December 30, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://vtv.vn/goc-khan-gia/co-gai-nha-nguoi-ta-phat-song-them-1-tap-tuan-20200205202114734.htm|title=\"C\u00f4 g\u00e1i nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta\" ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng th\u00eam 1 t\u1eadp/tu\u1ea7n|publisher=vtv.vn|accessdate=February 6, 2020}}</ref>\n| ''[[:vi:C\u00f4 g\u00e1i nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta|C\u00f4 g\u00e1i nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta]]'' <br/><small>(The Girl Next Door)</small>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 25\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | VFC\n| Tr\u1ecbnh L\u00ea Phong (director); L\u00ea Huy\u1ec1n (writers); \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00fa, Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Oanh, Vi\u1ec7t B\u1eafc, H\u01b0\u01a1ng Giang, B\u00f9i B\u00e0i B\u00ecnh, Linh Hu\u1ec7, Ti\u1ebfn Quang, Vi\u1ec7t Hoa, Ti\u1ebfn L\u1ed9c, Tr\u1ecdng L\u00e2n, Anh Tu\u1ea5n, Quang Tr\u1ecdng...\n| ''C\u00f4 g\u00e1i nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta'' <br><small>(That Girl Next Door)</small><br><small>by Huy\u1ec1n PK</small></br>\n| Drama, Romance\n| \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |19 Mar\u2013present <br><small><ref>{{cite web|url=https://vtv.vn/goc-khan-gia/nha-tro-balanha-noi-song-co-gai-nha-nguoi-ta-tren-vtv3-20200304110946838.htm|title=\"Nh\u00e0 tr\u1ecd Balanha\" n\u1ed1i s\u00f3ng \"C\u00f4 g\u00e1i nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta\" tr\u00ean VTV3|publisher=vtv.vn|accessdate=March 4, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://vtv.vn/goc-khan-gia/nha-tro-balanha-chinh-thuc-len-song-vtv3-20200318164147406.htm|title=\"Nh\u00e0 tr\u1ecd Balanha\" ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean s\u00f3ng VTV3|publisher=vtv.vn|accessdate=March 19, 2020}}</ref>\n| ''[[:vi:Nh\u00e0 tr\u1ecd Balanha|Nh\u00e0 tr\u1ecd Balanha]]'' <br/><small>(Homestay Balanha)</small>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 30\n| style=\"text-align:center